subject: Problem with after and before
msgSnippet: I work with J2se 5.0, eclipse 3.2. Problem the methods: @org.junit.BeforeClass public void InitTest() { System.out.println( ESTO AL Inicio DEL TEST ); }
messageBody:
I work with J2se 5.0, eclipse 3.2.
Problem the methods:

@...
public void InitTest() {
System.out.println("ESTO AL Inicio DEL TEST");

}

@AfterClass
public void endTest() {
System.out.println("ESTO AL FINAL DEL TEST");
}

Are not they never executed for that?
